  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-8 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Operating envelope is explicitly bounded (flow 2–6 L/min, speed 2400–3600 RPM, hematocrit 35–45%). Validation experiments densely cover the declared envelope at 15 flow-speed combinations. All 13 credibility factors assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels. Decision: Accepted.",
