      "type": "OperatingEnvelope",
      "name": "VAD centrifugal pump operating envelope",
      "description": "Flow rate: 2.0–6.0 L/min (increments of 1 L/min validated at 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 L/min). Rotational speed: 2400–3600 RPM (validated at 2400, 2800, 3200, 3600 RPM). Hematocrit: 35–45% (validated at 35%, 40%, 45%). Fluid temperature: 36–38 °C. Inlet pressure: 5–15 mmHg. Geometry tolerance: ±0.05 mm on all critical impeller dimensions per manufacturing inspection records. All 15 flow-speed combinations within this envelope have corresponding experimental hemolysis measurements used for validation."
    },
    "hasApplicabilityConstraint": {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/cou/cou2-vad/applicability-constraint",
